Why not working?

Have an extension, use the following code:

```
const quickPick = vscode.window.createQuickPick<T>();
quickPick.title = 'My Title;
quickPick.placeholder = placeholder;
quickPick.items = items;

quickPick.buttons = [{
		iconPath: vscode.ThemeIcon.File,
		tooltip: 'Learn More'
}];

quickPick.show();
```

Notice the quick pick appears broken showing a custom button

fyi @chrmarti

Report Issue to prefill these.
- VSCode Version: 1.33.1
- OS Version: macOS 10.14.2

Steps to Reproduce:

1. save the following as test `schema.json`:
```json
{
    "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "num": {
            "type": "number",
            "multipleOf": 0.1
        }
    }
}
```

2. define a `test.json`:
```json
{
   "num": 0.7
}
```

3. set settings to let VSCode load schema for `test.json`:
```json
{
    "json.schemas": [
        {
            "fileMatch": [
                "/test.json"
            ],
            "url": "file:///path/to/schema.json"
        },
    ]
}
```

Then you will see green squiggles under `0.7`, and output problems shows `Value is not devisible by 0.1`. Integer values like `3` also fails. 

However some other values like `0.8` is fine.
